Traditional OTA:

Centralized servers (AWS, Google Cloud)
Single point of failure
Can be censored/deleted
Trust required
STC Ultimate + IPFS:

Decentralized storage
Permanent, immutable records
Verifiable by anyone
Zero trust architecture
Formula untuk paper:

Storage_cost = C_ipfs + C_gas_cid
Where:

C_ipfs = IPFS pinning cost (~$0.001 per MB/month)
C_gas_cid = Gas to store CID on-chain (~$0.50)
Total < $1 vs. Traditional Cloud Storage + Verification Overhead!

KESIMPULAN:

âœ… Blockchain = Trust, verification, ownership
âœ… IPFS = Cheap, scalable storage for large data
âœ… Combined = Unstoppable, verifiable tourism platform
